# Report Metadata Verification Gate

When data-model changes affect entities/attributes/relations/source keys:

1. Validate reporting metadata (for example via `/api/reports/metadata`).
2. Confirm payloads match backend schemas and source registries.
3. Fix mismatches in the same change set.
4. State in final notes whether check passed (or why it was not required).
